  "instructions": {
    "text_instructions": [
      {
        "id": "bcfb74b376a54a5a0000000000000000",
        "content": [
          "## Winback Score Formula (0–100 points)\n",
          "\n",
          "The `winback_score` column in `churn_winback_recent_targets` is a composite score summing 5 components. It measures how worthwhile and likely it is to win back a churning user.\n",
          "\n",
          "### 1. Value Component (0–30 pts)\n",
          "Formula: LEAST(30, ltv_proxy / 100 * 5)\n",
          "- `ltv_proxy` = user's historical lifetime value in USD (cumulative commissions/spreads generated).\n",
          "- Awards 5 points per $100 of LTV, capped at 30.\n",
          "- A user with LTV >= $600 maxes out at 30 pts.\n",
          "- You can recover ltv_proxy from expected_ltv: when expected_ltv > 5, ltv_proxy ≈ expected_ltv / 0.3.\n",
          "\n",
          "### 2. Engagement Component (0–20 pts)\n",
          "Formula: LEAST(20, total_trades / 50 * 20)\n",
          "- `total_trades` = count of closed positions (excl. partial close children) since 2023.\n",
          "- A user with >= 50 trades gets full 20 pts. Someone with 10 trades gets 4 pts.\n",
          "\n",
          "### 3. Recency Component (0–20 pts)\n",
          "Tiered by `days_since_last_trade`:\n",
          "- <= 7 days: 20 pts\n",
          "- <= 14 days: 16 pts\n",
          "- <= 30 days: 12 pts\n",
          "- <= 60 days: 8 pts\n",
          "- <= 90 days: 4 pts\n",
          "- > 90 days: 0 pts\n",
          "\n",
          "### 4. Loss Resilience (0–15 pts)\n",
          "Tiered by `loss_rate` (% of closed trades that were losers):\n",
          "- < 40%: 15 pts\n",
          "- 40-49%: 12 pts\n",
          "- 50-59%: 8 pts\n",
          "- 60-69%: 4 pts\n",
          "- >= 70%: 0 pts\n",
          "Users who lost less are more likely to return.\n",
          "\n",
          "### 5. Deposit Commitment (0–15 pts)\n",
          "Formula: LEAST(15, total_deposits_usd / 5000 * 15)\n",
          "- `total_deposits_usd` = lifetime cumulative deposits.\n",
          "- $5,000+ maxes this out. Measures \"skin in the game\".\n",
          "\n",
          "### 6. Last Login \n",
          "Use `main`.`mixpanel`.`login_events` table to get the logins\n",
          "\n",
          "\n",
          "### Worked Examples\n",
          "- CID 22515431 (Score 96, inactive_14d): Value=30 (ltv~$2,697) + Engagement=20 (>=50 trades) + Recency=16 (<=14d) + Loss Resil.=15 (loss<40%) + Deposit=15 (deposits>=$5K) = 96\n",
          "- CID 27524308 (Score 50, inactive_30d): Value=0 (ltv~0) + Engagement=20 (>=50 trades) + Recency=12 (<=30d) + Loss Resil.=15 (loss<40%) + Deposit=3 (deposits~$987) = 50\n",
          "- CID 46933959 (Score 14.9, inactive_30d): Value=0 (ltv~0) + Engagement=0.8 (~2 trades) + Recency=12 (<=30d) + Loss Resil.=0 (loss>=70%) + Deposit=2.1 (deposits~$709) = 14.9\n",
          "\n",
          "### Other Columns\n",
          "- `expected_ltv` = estimated LTV on reactivation (ltv_proxy * 0.3 for users with LTV > 0; fixed fallback for others).\n",
          "- `budget_to_winback` = cost per reactivation attempt, based on value_tier (high=50, mid=30, low=15, else=8).\n",
          "- `reason_for_churn_prediction` = diagnostic label based on churn_state, loss_rate, stopout_rate, sentiment, and withdrawal behavior.\n",
          "- `incentive_type` = 'stock_airdrop' for Stocks/ETF users, 'cash_bonus' for others.\n",
          "- `pct_deposits_withdrawn` = recent_withdrawal_usd / total_deposits_usd * 100 (how much of lifetime deposits was cashed out in last 3 weeks).\n",
          "- Users in this table withdrew > 50% of their total deposits in the last 3 weeks."
        ]
